t 入去屌佢老母 而毋須參與分化討論。<br />\n鍵盤戰士應努力推正經post 例如準備事項去抵擋三毛攻勢。<br />\n三毛會開一啲反共post 減低大家戒心 請細心思考現時網絡上所有言論。<br />\n一般市民應少上連登 關電視 而休養等待今午遊行。<br />\n鬼得一隻 林奠 其他完全唔重要 。</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZB4gyv7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZB4gyv7.gif&h=7cacc0df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fbf57fba812b5d0c25b1e4edf73b8cefabf04c83","tid":1191973,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8ed51b36a2e72d5b1dd53667fcacb5446bbc849e","tid":1191973,"uid":253174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:50:49.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n黑衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n白衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T01:21:31.000Z","msg":"用腦諗下都知朝早梗係著白色衫啦<br />\n<br />\n後續行動先黑色都唔遲<br />\n<br />\n6月9號遊行嘅方針:兄弟爬山，各自努力，避免割席，拒絕篤灰，不打飛機，不傳耳語，不搞抹黑<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1192414\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1192414</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ccbbcd191085a588e004b096fafa6bded4cf4c39","tid":1191973,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T04:41:15.000Z","msg":"我著左黑色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68a46d5d5b0fc66cdda9c2d4ba1e55cb32e7f2b6","tid":1191973,"uid":13586,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T04:43:05.000Z","msg":"理得你咩色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有心自然會去<br />\n<br />\n利申：灰"},{"pid":"2336dfd81e6fb0db721c4662126cfd2140fa6603","tid":1191973,"uid":12254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T04:44:13.000Z","msg":"有太陽的時後白色"}]}